I could care less what guild tag they do, or do not have. Yes, I think that you represent your guild, but stop the &quot;this guild is more uber than this guild&quot; junk! Keep the thread on topic. If you wish to stir up trouble and bait flames, go to the Karana board. <p><img src="http://www.talonswitch.com/qamcard.jpg"><br>
