<br>
Everyone may not agree on everything, but that's why we have long discussions. It's like the Int's from LoTR (love that book/movie). It takes a long time to discuss things. Everyone add's their two cents, then someone add's their reply, etc. We eventually get to a conclusion, but it does take a while.<br>
<br>
I can't give you a good estimate. The problem currently is, instead of spending our time trying to fix the system, we are spending it dealing with the rogue group, or warding off flames. It may take weeks or months to get the new system going. But, things are being discussed. <p><img src="http://www.talonswitch.com/qamcard.jpg"><br>
